column148: Thank. Thank you for participating in our study.  If you wish to get VP hours, please send a scan of your VP sheet to epalme@uos.de. Remember also to include your individual code created at the beginning of the survey. The code has to be identical to the code created at the beginning. Otherwise, we will not be able to sign your VP hour sheet.  Your individual code consists of   	the third letter of your family name (e.g. SMITH --> I) 	the last number of your year of birth (e.g. 01.10.1990 --> 0) 	the last letter of your mother's first name (e.g. ANNE --> E)  	if not known, choose your own 	the first letter of your birth-place (e.g. BERLIN --> B) 	if not known, choose your current living place 	the number of your farther's birth date (e.g. 22 Oct 1975 --> 22) 	if not known, choose your own
